\c 43
\s Munyengetero kufambiswa nechiedza nezvokwadi yaJehovha
\p
\v 1 Nditongerei Mwari, mundireverere pamhosva yangu parudzi rusina tsitsi; Ndirwirei pamunhu anonyengera asina kururama.
\v 2 Nokuti ndimi Mwari simba rangu; mandirasireiko? Ndinofambireiko ndichichema nokuda
\s kwokumanikidza kwomuvengi?
\p
\v 3 Tumai chiedza chenyu nezvokwadi yenyu; zvinditungamirire; Zvindisvitse kugomo renyu dzvene, Nokutabhenakeri dzenyu.
\p
\v 4 Ipapo ndichasvika kuaritari yaMwari,
\s Kuna Mwari, iye mufaro wangu mukuru;
\s Ndichakurumbidzai nembira, imi Mwari,
\s Mwari wangu.
\p
\v 5 Unoshuwireiko, mweya wangu? Unoshaiwa rugare neiko mukati mangu?
\s Tarira kuna Mwari; nokuti
\s ndichazomurumbidza hangu, Iye muponesi wechiso changu,
\s naMwari wangu.
